snippet.title: 911 Operator Deluxe Edition Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Play through all available cities, events, calls, and reports! Unlock all equipment and vehicles! The complete 911 Operator collection in one neat package!

911 Operator Deluxe Edition includes:
- Base game
- Every Life Matters DLC
- Special Resources DLC
- Search & Rescue DLC
- First Response DLC

Official website: http://sonkagames.com/games/911-operator-deluxe-edition/
